description.narrative: UNICEF Tajikistan initiated and supported many CRC@30-related activities, events and consultations. In particular, the CO chose to use the CRC's birthday to launch, together with the Government, the national SDG programme for children. That event was convened by Deputy PM alongside every ministry and development partners. The occasion was also used to announce the new Champions for Children team of ambassadors - EU, UK, Saudi, Russian (and soon Japanese) ambassadors. Throughout 2019, UNICEF Tajikistan increasingly engaged key stakeholders from government, media and business to raise issues of children and win the public support for the cause of children. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/12/2019
